sub_title: Healthcare Nutrition Strategy Project Manager for CIS and Sri Lanka (Nutricia WorldWide, Danone) at Havas
summary:
Highly motivated, pro-active, open-minded, enthusiastic and creative Marketing & Communications professional with strong analytical skills and a diverse experience in project management; organizing and maintaining marketing and advertising campaigns and applying effective communications to improve streamline core operations in the company. 

I have more than 5 years of work experience as a Marketing Professional and Project Manager in Europe and Russia (Moscow). I would like to develop my career as a communication professional, project manager. Preferred industry: Healthcare Nutrition, Food, Pharma, Medicine, Marketing agency.

Key areas of interest include corporate communications, public relations, marketing, social media, advertising, brand management, media relations, journalism, psychology, different languages and intercultural exchange. 

Russian is my native language, full professional proficiency in English, learning Dutch.
